# WhatsApp Sales Concierge - Windsurf Development Rules

## Project Context

This is a multi-tenant SaaS platform providing AI-powered WhatsApp sales agents for SMEs. The system automates lead qualification, appointment booking, and customer engagement through WhatsApp using Claude/GPT.

**Tech Stack:**
- Next.js 15.1.11 (App Router) + TypeScript
- Supabase (PostgreSQL) with RLS
- Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4 (primary AI, 95% tool calling success)
- OpenAI GPT-4o (fallback, 70-80% tool calling success)
- Twilio (WhatsApp integration)
- Upstash Redis (background jobs)
- Vercel (deployment)

**Key Files:**
- `/src/lib/ai/agent.ts` - Main AI orchestrator
- `/src/lib/ai/tools/` - AI tool implementations
- `/src/lib/ai/prompts.ts` - System prompts
- `/src/lib/services/twilio/` - WhatsApp integration
- `/src/lib/services/calendar/` - Appointment system
- `/src/app/api/webhooks/twilio/` - Webhook handler

