## Core Architectural Principles

### 1. Multi-Tenant Isolation
- ALL database queries MUST include tenant_id filter
- Use Supabase RLS policies for data protection
- Never leak data across tenants
- Test tenant isolation in every feature

### 2. AI-First Design
- AI is the primary interface, not humans
- Design for conversation, not forms
- Tools are mandatory, not optional
- State must persist across conversation turns

### 3. Production Reliability
- Handle tool failures gracefully (retry + fallback)
- Log every tool execution with parameters
- Never leave users without a response
- Implement circuit breakers for external APIs

