## Database Query Optimization

**March 7, 2026 Performance Fix:**

**BEFORE (inefficient):**
```typescript
// Reload contact after EVERY tool call
async function processTools(tools) {
  for (const tool of tools) {
    await executeTool(tool);
    contact = await reloadContact(); // ❌ Unnecessary DB query
  }
}
```

**AFTER (optimized):**
```typescript
// Only reload contact after update_lead
async function processTools(tools) {
  for (const tool of tools) {
    await executeTool(tool);
    
    // Only reload if update_lead was called
    if (tool.name === 'update_lead') {
      contact = await reloadContact(); // ✅ Only when needed
    }
  }
}
```

**Result:** 50% reduction in DB queries

